Package: samsung-scripts
Replaces: nc10-scripts (<= 5.0~ppa9~nc10~karmic)
Depends: arandr, libnotify-bin
Architecture: all
Description: Scripts for Samsung netbooks
 This package contains useful scripts for Samsung netbooks.
 .
 These are the default keybindings:
 - FN-F4 --> Switch to the next screen layout.
 - FN-F5 --> Turn on/off the screen brightness.
 - FN-F7 --> Turn on/off the bluetooth.
 - FN-F8 --> Show CPU temperature and manage CPU governors.
 - FN-F9 --> Turn on/off the wireless card.
 - <Shift><Ctrl><Alt>w --> Turn on/off the webcam.
 - <Shift><Ctrl><Alt>m --> Toggle compiz on/off.
 .
 NOTE: On Ubuntu, make sure the 'commands' plugin is enabled in
 advanced compiz configuration, or else the hotkeys will not work.

Package: nc10-scripts
